{
  "id": "69e774187e06565a3c37704d",
  "title": "調声",
  "created": 1776776218,
  "updated": 1776777141,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69e774187e06565a3c37704d",
      "text": "調声",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776776218,
      "updated": 1776776218
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7741a000000000072bf3e",
      "text": " 歌声合成ソフトの歌声を調整すること",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776776218,
      "updated": 1776776852
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7766d000000000072bf6f",
      "text": " [調声]する前の状態は[ベタ打ち]と呼ばれる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776776813,
      "updated": 1776776813
    },
    {
      "id": "69e77685000000000072bf71",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776776837,
      "updated": 1776776837
    },
    {
      "id": "69e77673000000000072bf70",
      "text": "調声作業で行われること",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776776819,
      "updated": 1776776830
    },
    {
      "id": "69e77494000000000072bf49",
      "text": " 発音を調節したり、",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776776340,
      "updated": 1776776833
    },
    {
      "id": "69e77496000000000072bf4a",
      "text": "  自然な声に聞こえるように子音や母音の長さを調節する",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776776343,
      "updated": 1776776833
    },
    {
      "id": "69e77437000000000072bf41",
      "text": " 声の高さ(ピッチ)を曲線で描きこんだり、",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776776247,
      "updated": 1776776833
    },
    {
      "id": "69e774a7000000000072bf4b",
      "text": "  しゃくりを入れると強く歌う声になったり",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776776359,
      "updated": 1776776833
    },
    {
      "id": "69e77656000000000072bf5f",
      "text": "   [https://gyazo.com/56d6a72fb16cdc5f3a0a6d5c19c7e2dd]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776776791,
      "updated": 1776776833
    },
    {
      "id": "69e774d0000000000072bf4c",
      "text": "  ノート同士をゆるやかな曲線でつなぐと力の抜けた声になる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776776401,
      "updated": 1776777141
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7765a000000000072bf62",
      "text": "   [https://gyazo.com/c3677c379baeed3519eaf40bc23a8adc]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776776794,
      "updated": 1776776833
    },
    {
      "id": "69e77484000000000072bf44",
      "text": " genderやbreathnessなどのパラメーターを操作して声色を変えたりする",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776776325,
      "updated": 1776776833
    },
    {
      "id": "69e77485000000000072bf45",
      "text": "  ささやき声にしたり",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776776325,
      "updated": 1776776833
    },
    {
      "id": "69e77488000000000072bf46",
      "text": "  子供っぽい声にしたり",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776776328,
      "updated": 1776776833
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7748c000000000072bf47",
      "text": "  大人っぽい声にしたり",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1776776332,
      "updated": 1776776833
    },
    {
      "id": "69e77651000000000072bf59",
